results.description:
Building facade photo of the mensa building, a part of the municipal university campus in Amsterdam city. This image is located in the street Roeterstraat, as part of modern university architecture. Late evening sun is shining on the yellow brick facade and its reflecting windows. It is the light which is fascinating me in this picture. Huge plane trees are standing in front of the recent-built building for many more years! Urban nature! 

Amsterdam in free photos - urban photography of The Netherlands by Fons Heijnsbroek; Dutch street pictures of modern architecture, 6 September 2012
